    • Method Detail

      • get

        public T get()
        Retrieves the object contained in this holder.

        The first time this method is called, the Supplier passed to the #of(Supplier) method will be invoked to fetch the actual object. All following calls will then always return that same object.

        Returns:
        The object obtained from the initial Supplier this holder was constructd from.

      • of

        public static <T> Holder<T> of(Supplier<T> builder)
        Creates a new holder whose content will be retrieved from the given Supplier.
        Type Parameters:
        T - The type of object the returned holder will hold.
        Parameters:
        builder - The supplier from which the object contained in the holder will be obtained.
        Returns:
        A newly created holder.
